thread.title: Syrian state TV says Syrian air defences hit Israeli jets

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Syrian state TV says Syrian air defences hit Israeli jets
text:
BEIRUT (Reuters) - Syrian air defences opened fire in response to an Israeli act of “aggression” against a military base on Saturday and hit “more than one plane”, Syrian state media cited a military source as saying.
“The Israeli enemy entity at dawn today conducted a new aggression against one of the military bases in the central region. Our air defences confronted it and hit more than one plane,” the unidentified military source said.
Writing by Tom Perry; Editing by Paul Tait
